The Discord server ID
What data you want removed

Some moderation or banned server records may be kept if needed for safety, abuse prevention, or to protect the bot and its servers.

8. Children

Nyrix is intended for use on Discord and follows Discord’s age requirements. Users must meet the minimum age required by Discord and their country.

9. Security

Nyrix stores only the data needed for bot features. Reasonable steps are taken to protect stored data and bot access. No online service can be guaranteed to be completely secure.

10. Changes To This Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated when Nyrix changes features, data usage, hosting, or legal requirements. The latest version should always be the version linked on the bot’s Discord Developer Portal page or support server.

